      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REWARDS AND MORE (3) started favourite here last time, pushed forward and fought on bravely for a strong win. More weight but small field suits and the other pacemaker is scratched. Will take catching again. FLYING YISHU (1) kept coming and just missed to finish second in the same race. Meets the winner better at the weights and could well turn the tables. DELAGO LAD (4) dropped back to 1000m latest and after a moderate start never got into the race. The extra ground and small field suits and gets chance to atone. Was an open class winner the start prior. O'TYCOON (2) resumed here with a fourth behind REWARDS AND MORE and meets the winner better at the weights. Can feature in the finish. MATHEMATICS (7) is a veteran here and is next best.",
